star's wife,"],[1238,1368,"Renee Thompson,"],[1368,1476,"cuddling up"],[1476,1726,"with her husband's rival."],[1797,1901,"Let's see how you get out"],[1901,2127,"of this one, Renee."],[2323,2485,"Okay everyone, just a reminder,"],[2485,2698,"this is off the record, so"],[2698,2819,"no photos."],[2819,2873,"Our head"],[2873,3007,"coach will be making her"],[3007,3178,"official debut on match day"],[3178,3315,"in a few days time."],[3415,3561,"Fire away."],[3561,3636,"Ms. R!"],[3636,3732,"I've learned that you built"],[3732,3908,"a highly efficient, high tempo system"],[3908,4029,"with Edward Hughes"],[4029,4116,"leading the offense."],[4116,4233,"Could you elaborate on that?"],[4233,4362,"Well, the key is just keeping"],[4362,4600,"an aggressive forcecheck and-"],[5080,5334,"Ms. R, a reliable source claims"],[5334,5430,"you cheated on your husband"],[5430,5584,"with his rival."],[5584,5680,"Is that how you landed"],[5680,5834,"this coaching job?"],[5834,5989,"Wait, what?"]],"23":[[183,291,"Madeline."],[291,433,"Someone leaked the story about"],[433,500,"Renee cheating."],[500,679,"This is going to ruin Levi."],[679,859,"Everyone is going to be talking"],[859,1117,"about his wife betrayed him!"],[1117,1301,"Oh, that bitch!"],[1422,1559,"I can’t breathe!"],[1805,1901,"Nora!"],[2394,2481,"What happened?"],[2481,2606,"How did my mom pass out?"],[2606,2886,"She heard the news"],[2886,3103,"about Renee's affair."],[3103,3378,"And I guess"],[3378,3582,"she couldn't handle it."],[3582,3816,"Who the fuck leaked the story?"],[3816,4383,"Well... I, I think it was Renee herself"],[4383,4525,"who leaked it"],[4525,4771,"to try to get you to divorce her."],[4771,4917,"What a move, Renee."],[4917,5080,"You just crossed the line."],[5080,5130,"I should've"],[5130,5413,"never cut you any slack."],[5488,6493,"Ms. R! Ms. R!"],[6623,6769,"Everyone calm down."],[6769,6944,"Just calm down."],[6944,7069,"The truth is..."],[7524,7624,"The truth is..."]],"24":[[0,141,"Just calm down, all right?"],[141,204,"Calm down."],[204,342,"The truth is the Falcons–"],[342,433,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[433,517,"this press conference"],[517,583,"is canceled."],[583,742,"As head coach, my priority is"],[742,875,"and always will be the game."],[875,1034,"I'm not letting any off-ice drama"],[1034,1159,"impact my players."],[1222,1317,"I'll clear everything up"],[1317,1380,"after the game."],[1380,1618,"But until then, I ask for patience"],[1618,1747,"and respect."],[1843,1943,"You heard her."],[1943,2027,"Why are you still here?"],[2027,2085,"Let's move."],[2535,2698,"That lying bastard!"],[2698,2861,"He's the one cheating, not Renee."],[2882,3032,"I’ll sue him and everyone spreading"],[3032,3103,"this garbage."],[3103,3219,"I’ll blacklist the lot of them."],[3240,3374,"Chill out, big bro."],[3374,3561,"Your job is to focus on the game."],[3636,3737,"You need to make my coaching"],[3737,3924,"look good, remember?"],[3924,4041,"Both of you."],[4041,4175,"All right, all right."],[4175,4337,"Trust your judgment, seeing"],[4337,4533,"you were such a badass earlier."],[4533,4688,"And stop going so easy on Carlson."],[4688,4850,"He doesn't deserve it."],[4850,4946,"Relax."],[5009,5125,"I know what to do."],[5885,6001,"Hospital, now."],[6001,6147,"If you want that divorce."],[6339,6448,"Finally,"],[6448,6619,"it's time to end this nightmare."]],"25":[[200,371,"Did you sign the divorce papers?"],[371,529,"Renee,"],[529,700,"I can't even believe"],[700,804,"that you had the nerve"],[804,959,"to show up today"],[959,1192,"as the wife of a hockey star."],[1192,1372,"You have disrespected"],[1372,1493,"your mother-in-law,"],[1493,1572,"and you've cheated"],[1572,1668,"on your husband."],[1668,1801,"You may not care"],[1801,1935,"about your reputation,"],[2047,2210,"but Levi"],[2210,2431,"still has to live with this."],[2744,2923,"Couldn't wait to get rid of me?"],[2923,3011,"Even willing to trash"],[3011,3157,"your own reputation."],[3157,3282,"Oh, please."],[3282,3424,"If I wanted to force this divorce,"],[3424,3528,"I would have just exposed"],[3528,3657,"you and your little mistress"],[3657,3803,"and her sick little act"],[3803,4016,"to get all the attention."],[4016,4225,"Everyone is fed up with"],[4225,4366,"your little act."],[4366,4617,"No one believes your lies."],[4617,4742,"Lies?"],[4742,4975,"God, that's rich coming from you."],[4975,5080,"Do you remember how you claimed"],[5080,5138,"to help Levi"],[5138,5276,"when he was in a coma?"],[5276,5380,"And how you stole the credit"],[5380,5451,"from someone else"],[5451,5588,"to guilt trip Levi?"],[5880,6064,"What are you talking about?"],[6064,6197,"Madeline even tested"],[6197,6473,"electrical currents on herself for Levi."]],"26":[[0,129,"Madeline even tested"],[129,216,"electrical currents"],[216,421,"on herself for Levi."],[1384,1539,"Mrs. Carlson, stop!"],[1539,1672,"I know you’re worried"],[1672,1743,"about your husband,"],[1743,1989,"but this is a medical grade device."],[1989,2139,"Testing electrical currents on yourself"],[2139,2202,"could be dangerous."],[2202,2298,"It could kill you."],[2298,2394,"You've already passed out"],[2394,2473,"three times."],[2473,2660,"I know, doctor Lee,"],[2660,2777,"but I have to figure out a way"],[2777,2898,"to help Levi."],[2898,2969,"He's an athlete."],[2969,3169,"His muscles can't just waste away."],[3169,3324,"I really hope this works."],[3474,3541,"Everyone else has"],[3541,3653,"already given up."],[3653,3762,"Even his own mother."],[3762,3937,"And don't get me started on that"],[3937,4237,"negligent team doctor Madeline."],[4429,4650,"Say, how was your European"],[4650,4779,"vacation, Doc?"],[4779,4838,"Did you have fun"],[4838,4946,"when Levi was suffering?"],[4946,5171,"This woman is crazy!"],[5171,5292,"I never want to see her again."],[5292,5455,"Levi, get her out of here now!"],[5455,5559,"Just have your precious son"],[5559,5663,"sign the divorce papers,"],[5663,5805,"and I'll be on my way."],[5805,5922,"An ungrateful"],[5922,6114,"mother-in-law and a cheating husband."],[6172,6339,"I should be the one sick."],[6339,6464,"Oh!"],[7015,7203,"Levi, divorce this bitch immediately,"],[7203,7278,"or I swear"],[7278,7461,"I'm gonna drop dead right now."],[7590,7695,"Fine."],[7695,7878,"Let’s end this."]],"27":[[233,383,"Two million."],[383,563,"Should be enough to start fresh."],[600,742,"Get you a real job."],[1263,1347,"You can't live off"],[1347,1576,"the backs of men forever."],[2702,2873,"Keep your money."],[2873,2927,"You're going to need it"],[2927,3065,"to hire a personal coach."],[3065,3144,"I mean, as a defenseman,"],[3144,3311,"you are mediocre at best."],[3311,3453,"You are weak positioning,"],[3453,3586,"too slow on your feet."],[3586,3737,"Without my system covering your flaws,"],[3737,3824,"I don't even know what you’re gonna–"],[3824,4041,"Shut your fucking mouth!"],[4041,4179,"Who the hell do you think you are?"],[4179,4312,"Levi is the best player"],[4312,4383,"on his team."],[4383,4533,"Yeah, on his team."],[4533,4617,"But being the best"],[4617,4742,"on the Boston Seagulls is like"],[4742,4884,"being a fast seagull."],[5050,5150,"But the moment"],[5150,5372,"a real predator shows up?"],[5372,5505,"Say, the Falcons?"],[5622,5726,"You're just prey"],[5726,5901,"waiting to be picked off."],[5947,6135,"It's funny that you mention"],[6135,6252,"the Falcons."],[6252,6314,"Levi's"],[6314,6573,"been offered to sign with them."],[6573,6702,"Really?"],[6702,6819,"Aww, see,"],[6819,6915,"they may have an elite"],[6915,7102,"goalie like Clark Molson,"],[7102,7215,"but I don't think that coach"],[7215,7298,"is going to want to sign"],[7298,7532,"a... deadweight defenseman."],[7682,7816,"Right?"],[8016,8191,"The divorce papers are in my car."],[8312,8441,"Let's go and sign them."]],"28":[[1451,1555,"It's finally over."],[2302,2402,"What are you doing here?"],[2402,2544,"I came to celebrate your new life,"],[2544,2610,"my Queen."],[2769,2890,"Clark's already in the club."],[2890,3061,"We got to go celebrate!"],[3061,3178,"Thank you."],[3178,3261,"You're actually into this"],[3261,3415,"dumb teenager?"],[3415,3545,"We're divorced now."],[3545,3707,"My love life is not your concern."],[4191,4325,"Hey, Carlson."],[4325,4450,"Ever stop to think that maybe"],[4450,4587,"you didn’t treat this amazing woman"],[4587,4708,"the way you should have?"],[4708,4808,"You're going to regret that"],[4808,4896,"on the ice."],[4896,5042,"The day after tomorrow."],[5100,5238,"You hurt Renee,"],[5238,5326,"and I'm going to make you"],[5326,5422,"pay for that."]],"29":[[992,1188,"Did you take care of the news?"],[1188,1368,"Mr. Carlson, something's off."],[1368,1530,"All of the articles just vanished,"],[1530,1755,"like they never even existed."],[1755,1914,"Vanished?"],[1914,2168,"Who's behind it?"],[2168,2273,"It's the Molson Group,"],[2273,2494,"the owner of the Boston Falcons."],[2494,2777,"Molsons? Clark’s behind this?"],[2777,2873,"Mr. Carlson,"],[2873,3032,"the game is in two days."],[3032,3215,"You should get some rest."],[3215,3357,"By the way,"],[3357,3461,"I heard somebody helped test"],[3461,3611,"the electrical currents on me,"],[3611,3749,"while I was in my coma."],[3749,3974,"Find out who exactly."],[3974,4179,"I want to thank them."],[4179,4325,"In person."],[5171,5267,"Finally,"],[5267,5422,"Renee and Levi aren’t"],[5422,5563,"together anymore."],[5563,5663,"From now on,"],[5663,5876,"I'm the only one by his side."],[5876,6056,"Just as it should be."],[6360,6443,"Oh my God,"],[6443,6552,"Edward Hughes is here!"],[6552,6810,"Oh damn, he’s so hot!"]],"30":[[425,625,"She's gorgeous."],[625,754,"Is she with Edward?"],[754,871,"Supporting her boyfriend"],[871,955,"at his game?"],[955,1038,"That's adorable."],[1038,1159,"Hashtag couple goals."],[1159,1376,"Levi, look!"],[1376,1710,"Isn't that Renee with Edward?"],[1710,1776,"I heard"],[1776,1968,"she's Levi Carlson's ex-wife."],[1968,2077,"But isn't she..."],[2077,2223,"a little out of his league?"],[2223,2323,"Wow."],[2323,2427,"Already divorced,"],[2427,2552,"and she’s front and center"],[2552,2786,"at her new man's game."],[2786,2827,"Looks like"],[2827,2948,"Renee has Edward"],[2948,3211,"wrapped around her finger."],[3211,3511,"Shut the fuck up, Maddie."],[3703,3803,"I've got to convince"],[3803,3978,"Ms. R to sign Levi!"],[3978,4133,"So he can forget about that"],[4133,4433,"bitch, and be with me."]],"31":[[675,871,"Oh, she's the new head coach?"],[871,992,"She looks young."],[992,1247,"Is she really as good as they say?"],[1551,1743,"Whoa, whoa, whoa."],[1743,1885,"We're here to see Ms. R."],[1885,2043,"My son is Levi Carlson."],[2043,2285,"We're here to get Ms. R to sign Levi."],[2285,2481,"The bench area is only open to"],[2481,2615,"to coaches and players."],[2615,2736,"You can make an appointment"],[2736,2919,"with Ms. R after the game."],[2919,3003,"Oh, really?"],[3003,3111,"If that's the case, then"],[3111,3203,"what is that"],[3203,3382,"woman doing over there?"],[3382,3549,"So you give bench access to"],[3549,3849,"gold diggers, but not to family?"],[3849,4012,"Let me ask you something."],[4012,4162,"Did she bribe you,"],[4162,4408,"or sleep her way in?"],[4408,4575,"What are you even talking about?"],[4575,4829,"That’s Ms. R, the head coach."]],"32":[[321,567,"Seriously, the only thing that woman"],[567,696,"is qualified to do"],[696,967,"is babysit for free."],[967,1209,"Now, let me at her and I will expose"],[1209,1359,"the fraud myself!"],[2031,2235,"Wow, what are you doing here?"],[2235,2485,"We're here on official business."],[2485,2706,"Unlike some gold diggers"],[2706,2831,"who just want to sleep"],[2831,2915,"with the men."],[2915,3023,"Watch your mouth."],[3023,3111,"Listen, Renee,"],[3111,3174,"if you'd like to"],[3174,3286,"make yourself useful,"],[3286,3382,"why don't you just show us"],[3382,3528,"where Ms. R is?"],[3528,3753,"I'd like to discuss signing Levi."],[3753,3887,"Oh, yeah?"],[3887,4045,"Treat Renee like shit, and you expect"],[4045,4362,"the Falcons to sign Levi just like that?"],[4362,4575,"Like her opinion matters?"],[4575,4650,"Even if she is"],[4650,4821,"your little mistress."],[4821,4971,"Yeah, exactly."],[4971,5130,"Ms. R is a genius."],[5130,5309,"She'd be a fool not to sign Levi."],[5309,5372,"He's the best"],[5372,5588,"defenseman in the NHA."],[5588,5709,"Should I just tell them the truth?"],[5839,5910,"People like this"],[5910,6110,"don't deserve the truth."],[6110,6293,"But, since you are so confident"],[6293,6477,"in Levi's abilities,"],[6477,6519,"what do you say"],[6519,6710,"we make this interesting?"],[6710,6861,"If Levi can stop Edward,"],[6861,7086,"the Falcon star center,"],[7086,7286,"then I will personally convince"],[7286,7511,"Ms. R to draft that contract."],[7511,7607,"But if Edward scores,"],[7607,7674,"you two are banned"],[7674,7899,"from the Molson Center forever."],[7899,8041,"Deal?"]],"33":[[58,279,"Oh, look at the little gold-digging slut"],[279,575,"making deals for Ms. R herself."],[575,629,"No."],[629,855,"I'd like to speak to her directly."],[855,921,"All right."],[921,1013,"I've had enough of this."],[1013,1176,"The Ms. R that you've been looking"],[1176,1355,"for is standing right here."],[1355,1589,"Renee is the new head"],[1589,1810,"coach of the Falcons."],[2306,2498,"Please! This woman is nothing"],[2498,2844,"but an uneducated orphan."],[2844,3061,"A housewife!"],[3061,3211,"You really expect me to believe"],[3211,3311,"that she's some"],[3311,3520,"hockey strategy genius?"],[3520,3645,"Give that back!"],[3991,4112,"Let go of my Mom!"],[4212,4391,"She started it."],[4391,4504,"What are you even doing here?"],[4504,4713,"This area is for players and coaches."],[4713,4829,"Yeah, Renee,"],[4829,4971,"you shouldn't even be here."],[4971,5125,"Yeah! Security, get this woman"],[5125,5267,"out of here immediately!"],[5267,5401,"Get your hands off of her!"],[5501,5684,"Good afternoon."],[5684,5780,"I'm sure you've all heard"],[5780,5951,"plenty of stories about the Boston"],[5951,6089,"Falcons' new coach."],[6089,6185,"Well, it's time"],[6185,6377,"for the official introduction."],[6377,6677,"The tactical mastermind..."],[6710,6869,"Ms. R!"],[7478,7545,"Hi, everyone."],[7545,7699,"I am Ms. R, the new head coach"],[7699,7887,"of the Falcons."]],"34":[[558,696,"Mom, I want to be a coach"],[696,859,"like Ms. R, too!"],[859,934,"Oh my God,"],[934,1130,"the first female coach in the NHA"],[1130,1192,"ever!"],[1192,1284,"She's so gorgeous"],[1284,1443,"and so confident."],[1518,1789,"You ungrateful little bitch."],[1789,1968,"You just divorced Levi,"],[1968,2064,"and now you're here"],[2064,2243,"siding with his rivals?"],[2719,2840,"How dare you?"],[2898,2990,"Renee?"],[3232,3361,"I finally signed with a team"],[3361,3520,"who respects me."],[3520,3616,"Problem?"],[3616,3732,"Respect?"],[3732,3883,"We know how you earned"],[3883,4024,"that little position."],[4024,4250,"Oh, yeah, Renee."],[4250,4491,"Sleeping with the entire team?"],[4491,4612,"That's a new low."],[4612,4746,"Even for you."],[4746,4875,"You could get diseases."],[4875,4971,"You know not everyone has to"],[4971,5117,"sleep their way to success?"],[5230,5347,"You!"],[5409,5547,"Get off of her."]],"35":[[37,241,"Hey, what's going on?"],[337,517,"Hey, hey! I’m–"],[579,775,"I am still meant to be here!"],[775,909,"This is a public arena,"],[909,1038,"you can't just do that, okay?"],[1038,1205,"Why the change in attitude now?"],[1205,1259,"Where was all that"],[1259,1405,"when you were bullying Renee?"],[1405,1547,"You're so fake!"],[1547,1676,"Once we hit the ice,"],[1676,1730,"you're going to pay"],[1730,1914,"for everything you did to Renee."],[1914,2110,"You old-ass fucking grandpa."],[2756,2965,"Renee is nothing but a housewife,"],[2965,3094,"she doesn't know shit!"],[3094,3232,"Don't be fooled by her."],[3232,3336,"Yeah, you don't know who"],[3336,3461,"you're messing with!"],[3720,3941,"Who the hell are you to judge Ms. R.?"],[3941,4170,"I am Levi’s mother, that’s who!"],[4170,4350,"And I'm-"],[4441,4579,"Hey."],[4579,4750,"You okay, Sis?"],[4750,4892,"They didn't hurt you, did they?"],[4892,5046,"No, no. I'm fine."],[5046,5288,"I know how to protect myself."],[5288,5384,"The match will begin"],[5384,5480,"in one minute."],[5480,5580,"All right,"],[5580,5672,"come on, let's get out there."],[5672,5797,"Let’s kick some ass!"],[6014,6247,"Go Falcons!"]],"36":[[1426,1514,"Let’s go!"],[2919,3044,"Agh!"],[3445,3545,"Go Hughes!"],[5588,6006,"So, you don't care about me at all now,"],[6006,6160,"Renee?"],[7261,7415,"Yeah!"]],"37":[[383,504,"I mean, I think we played really well."],[504,679,"I think Levi Carlson talks a lot, but"],[679,746,"I mean, when it actually"],[746,842,"comes down to playing,"],[842,925,"we actually perform."],[925,1013,"And he does a lot of talking."],[1013,1101,"Dragging me in here"],[1101,1255,"like a playground bully?"],[1255,1484,"Such a sore loser, Mr. Carlson."],[1484,1647,"You love playing dirty, don't you?"],[1647,1755,"Playing dirty?"],[1755,1885,"It's called strategy."],[1885,2043,"You know, the thing that coaches do?"],[2043,2127,"Finding out the other"],[2127,2256,"team's weaknesses."],[2256,2364,"Really?"],[2364,2439,"Was this your plan"],[2439,2594,"the entire time?"],[2594,2790,"What?"],[2790,2957,"Was that why you married me?"],[2957,3065,"Not for the love,"],[3065,3178,"not for the money,"],[3178,3315,"but to study me?"],[3315,3457,"Break me down play by play?"],[3457,3561,"Move by move?"],[3561,3645,"Pathetic."],[3645,3712,"You really are"],[3712,3916,"a self-centered asshole."],[3916,4095,"You think you're so special"],[4095,4241,"that I would trash my marriage"],[4241,4346,"for some cheap advantage"],[4346,4491,"in a game?"],[4491,4608,"You know what, if that’s how you see"],[4608,4671,"me, let's just pretend we don’t"],[4671,4783,"know each other."],[4825,4946,"Renee–"]],"38":[[150,271,"Of course."],[271,396,"All three goals I scored"],[396,550,"today were for our new coach."],[550,638,"She’s one of the most"],[638,788,"important people in my life."],[788,1038,"All I care about is making her happy."],[2402,2498,"What the fuck, Carlson?"],[2498,2744,"Stop harassing my wife, prick."],[2744,2936,"She's not your wife anymore, old man."],[2936,2994,"Oh yeah?"],[2994,3036,"Hey!"],[3107,3311,"Hey, what the hell is going on?"]],"39":[[20,208,"Ms. R, is it true that you cheated on Levi"],[208,400,"with Edward during your marriage?"],[400,592,"No, Mr. Carlson and I officially divorced"],[592,721,"a few days ago."],[721,859,"Let me be clear."],[859,1059,"I never cheated."],[1059,1247,"Edward and I are simply friends."],[1247,1372,"But according to my sources–"],[1372,1480,"Before marrying Levi,"],[1480,1539,"I was Edward's coach"],[1539,1655,"at the academy."],[1655,1780,"A special bond, yes,"],[1780,2006,"but that's all it was."],[2006,2173,"So..."],[2173,2335,"Renee never cheated."],[2335,2406,"And for those of you"],[2406,2473,"questioning how"],[2473,2644,"I even got this job,"],[2644,2857,"check my record at the academy."],[2857,3053,"The stats speak for themselves."],[3053,3174,"And for today's strategy,"],[3278,3490,"it's already been posted online."],[3490,3545,"I don't mind"],[3545,3741,"our opponents studying it."],[3741,3949,"In fact, I love a good challenge."],[3949,4262,"So she didn't target me?"],[4262,4583,"I wasn't even worth focusing on."],[4583,4829,"Coach Renee is a mentor in my life,"],[4829,4913,"and I won't stand"],[4913,5063,"for the disrespect."],[5063,5171,"If that game wasn't enough"],[5171,5313,"to prove how good she is,"],[5313,5563,"then we'll just prove it in the finals."],[5830,5910,"I think there's been"],[5910,6185,"a big misunderstanding."],[6185,6293,"My wife and I"],[6293,6439,"are still clearly together, I–"],[6961,7148,"Somebody call help!"]],"40":[[308,471,"Hey, what's wrong with you?"],[471,633,"Why did you scare her like that?"],[633,779,"This is all your fault."],[779,996,"Your hands were all over my wife."],[996,1188,"I swear to God, if anything happens–"],[1188,1413,"She's not your wife anymore."],[1547,1634,"You asshole!"],[1634,1839,"Would you two grow up?"],[1935,2077,"How’s Renee doing?"],[2202,2273,"Doctor Lee."],[2273,2381,"Renee!"],[2381,2569,"Renee is fine, just low blood sugar."],[2569,2731,"Probably from overworking"],[2731,2865,"and not getting enough rest."],[2865,2919,"Combined"],[2919,3069,"with the previous miscarriage"],[3069,3207,"and the testing"],[3207,3357,"from the electrical current-"],[3357,3470,"Wait..."],[3566,3741,"Electrical testing?"],[3741,3866,"What are you talking about?"],[3866,4020,"While you were in a coma,"],[4020,4120,"Renee insisted"],[4120,4266,"on testing the electrical currents"],[4266,4425,"on herself first."],[4425,4592,"We warned her about the risks,"],[4592,4692,"the potential long term"],[4692,4859,"effects on her body..."]],"41":[[0,271,"We warned her about the risks."],[271,400,"Mr. Carlson,"],[400,579,"everyone gave up on you back then,"],[579,696,"including your own mother"],[696,880,"and the team doctor, Madeline."],[880,984,"Renee was the only one"],[984,1209,"still staying by your side."],[1272,1447,"Thank you, doctor."],[2102,2206,"What have I done?"],[2206,2381,"I'm such an idiot."],[2381,2531,"She did all this for me?"],[2531,2715,"And what did I give her in return?"],[2715,2902,"Nothing."],[2902,3203,"Nothing but pain."],[3290,3453,"Renee,"],[3453,3724,"our divorce was a mistake."],[3724,3887,"I'll fix everything..."],[3995,4158,"and we will get back together"],[4158,4362,"when I do."]],"42":[[0,175,"Oh, Nora."],[175,325,"What are we going to do?"],[325,417,"What if Levi doesn't"],[417,554,"want to marry me anymore?"],[554,663,"Oh, please."],[663,754,"I will never let"],[754,850,"him get back together"],[850,980,"with that bitch."],[980,1359,"Besides, Levi will be all yours,"],[1405,1705,"once he drinks this."],[2544,2686,"Oh, Levi."],[2686,2790,"We need to go, let’s go."],[2790,2898,"Levi!"],[2898,3090,"Be gentle with Madeline."],[3090,3153,"You know that"],[3153,3257,"ever since she tested"],[3257,3374,"that device on herself for you,"],[3374,3545,"she's had nothing but problems."],[3649,3799,"Yeah, ow!"],[3799,3862,"You’ve been taking care of me"],[3862,3966,"all this time?"],[3966,4058,"Really?"],[4058,4187,"Levi Carlson,"],[4187,4350,"that is no way to treat the woman"],[4350,4437,"who took care of you"],[4437,4579,"while you were in your coma!"],[4579,4746,"Then what are these?"],[5017,5109,"You've been taking credit"],[5109,5321,"for everything that Renee did."],[5321,5601,"No, no, I can explain this."],[5601,5797,"Uh, these documents"],[5797,6097,"were obviously forged by Renee,"],[6097,6243,"to frame me."],[6306,6464,"Renee is just someone"],[6464,6564,"who sleeps around"],[6564,6690,"for opportunities."],[6690,6956,"I won't let her use my son again."],[6956,7073,"I have to make sure"],[7073,7361,"she and Levi are done for good!"]],"43":[[0,70,"Levi!"],[70,283,"Levi, please calm down."],[283,467,"Here, have a glass of water"],[467,608,"and we will talk this through."],[608,771,"Come on, you need to hydrate."],[771,821,"Water?"],[821,875,"Yeah."],[875,988,"You're dehydrated."],[988,1088,"Jesus."],[3190,3269,"We're going to make"],[3269,3545,"you mine, sweetheart."],[3545,3707,"Renee..."],[3707,3899,"No."],[3899,4308,"Renee cheated on you."],[4308,4608,"She abandoned you."],[4654,4954,"But now you can be mine..."],[4954,5171,"forever."],[5171,5301,"Maddie?"],[5301,5409,"Maddie, get off me."],[5409,5522,"Levi, come on,"],[5522,5618,"you’re being dramatic! - Maddie..."],[5618,5805,"Let go. I said let go!"],[5805,5880,"Uh!"],[6481,6644,"I've never loved you."],[6644,6940,"I've only had love for Renee."],[6940,7032,"Levi..."],[7032,7228,"Can’t you see?"],[7228,7490,"I am the only woman"],[7490,7674,"good enough for you..."],[7770,8008,"We should be together..."],[8008,8258,"Not you and Renee!"],[9013,9238,"Maddie, even if I was drugged..."],[9238,9446,"I would never touch you."],[9847,10010,"Shit!"],[10218,10431,"Renee doesn't even love you."],[10431,10623,"You hear that?"],[10623,10789,"Levi?"],[10923,11090,"Renee..."],[11090,11244,"you are the only woman"],[11244,11473,"I've ever wanted,"],[11473,11774,"and the only one I ever will."],[12066,12149,"I wish"],[12149,12383,"you could give me a second chance."]],"44":[[112,246,"Thank you."],[867,980,"Look, if you have something to say,"],[980,1096,"can you just say it?"],[1096,1234,"I’m needed back at the rink soon."],[1534,1693,"Renee, I know I messed up."],[1693,1856,"I was a total jerk."],[1856,1918,"Was?"],[1918,2177,"Renee, I'm serious."],[2177,2302,"I'm sorry."],[2431,2544,"Thank you for taking care of me"],[2544,2677,"during my coma."],[2677,2744,"I didn't realize"],[2744,2911,"all the things you did for me."],[3107,3382,"And all the awful things I said."],[3382,3616,"I'm sorry."],[3616,3745,"Look..."],[3745,3974,"it's water under the bridge."],[3974,4041,"Let's just be sure"],[4041,4341,"not to meet in private again."],[5722,5889,"Well, if that's all, I’ll be on my way..."],[5889,5955,"No–"],[6160,6285,"Renee, the reason why I asked"],[6285,6460,"you here today is because..."],[6631,6694,"I was hoping we could"],[6694,6794,"get back together."]],"45":[[446,575,"What the hell are you doing?"],[905,1288,"Why do you care so much about her?"],[1476,1776,"Because she's my wife."],[1830,2022,"If you come after her again,"],[2022,2235,"I'll make sure you regret it."],[2235,2344,"Security!"],[2344,2431,"Kick her out!"],[2431,2569,"She’s banned from every restaurant"],[2569,2673,"I invest in."],[2777,2944,"Levi, I..."],[2944,3053,"Renee!"],[3053,3249,"You bitch! You’re trying to steal"],[3249,3453,"Levi away from me."],[3453,3603,"I won't let you do this."],[3603,3753,"Don’t act like I don’t know"],[3753,3883,"what you’re doing!"],[5125,5196,"No, hey."],[5196,5380,"You don't have to do that."],[5497,5559,"Are you all right?"],[5559,5709,"I'm fine, just..."],[5709,5822,"Go get your girlfriend."],[5822,6010,"I'll get a taxi."],[6101,6381,"Madeline’s not my girlfriend."],[6381,6648,"She never was."],[6648,6948,"Renee..."],[7273,7549,"You were always my first choice."],[8053,8141,"Hey!"],[9572,9751,"Hey."],[9751,9897,"I need you to take care of someone"],[9897,9964,"for me."],[9964,10260,"Renee Thompson."],[10260,10347,"Yeah."],[10347,10568,"Same as before."],[10568,10698,"Make it look like..."],[10698,10802,"an accident."]],"46":[[629,754,"Here."],[855,942,"No."],[942,1063,"Keep it."],[1063,1134,"No, really."],[1134,1251,"I have a change of clothes in the car,"],[1251,1359,"it’s okay."],[1359,1493,"But, um..."],[1493,1755,"Thank you, Levi."],[1755,1943,"I'll see you at the next game?"],[1943,2093,"As a rival?"],[2189,2427,"Wait."],[2427,2635,"Renee..."],[2635,2736,"There's something"],[2736,3036,"I wanted to ask you."],[4208,4295,"Oh my God."],[4354,4433,"Levi?"],[4471,4579,"Levi!"],[4579,4767,"Help! Somebody help!"],[4767,4946,"Somebody call 911!"]],"47":[[1046,1172,"There's quite a lot of bleeding,"],[1172,1309,"but luckily it's all external."],[1309,1376,"He just needs about"],[1376,1555,"a week of rest."],[3224,3349,"Hey, Clark, I need you to"],[3349,3570,"run a license plate for me."],[3570,3645,"There was an accident when"],[3645,3858,"I was at the restaurant with Levi."],[3858,3941,"No, no, no, no."],[3941,4104,"I’m, I'm alright, I just..."],[4258,4437,"He was hurt because of me."],[4550,4675,"Thank you."],[4675,4783,"Thank you, thank you, thank you."],[4783,4900,"You're the best."],[4900,5150,"So that's why you rejected Edward..."],[5150,5288,"Because your heart"],[5288,5409,"belongs to..."],[5409,5588,"Clark?"]],"48":[[342,633,"How dare you touch my sister."],[633,800,"You out of your mind?"],[800,938,"Mr. Molson..."],[938,1205,"I didn't know Renee was your sister."],[1205,1288,"Please let me go."],[1288,1472,"I was just following orders."],[1472,1768,"Who's behind this?"],[1847,2110,"Tell me who's behind this,"],[2110,2310,"and maybe"],[2310,2610,"I'll spare your life."],[2656,2786,"It was..."],[3215,3345,"Perfect."],[3345,3545,"I’ll make sure this little criminal act"],[3545,3749,"is exposed on the biggest stage."]],"49":[[1038,1159,"Clark, what are you doing here?"],[1159,1255,"What are you doing?"],[1255,1359,"You nannying him again?"],[1359,1409,"What are you talking about?"],[1409,1497,"No, I'm not here"],[1497,1559,"because I'm thinking about"],[1559,1701,"getting back together with him."],[1701,1876,"He got injured because of me."],[2014,2164,"Coach, we got a bit of a situation"],[2164,2256,"back at the club."],[2256,2464,"Boss wants me to come pick you up."],[2602,2744,"I'm all right."],[2744,2827,"Go."],[2827,2957,"I don't want you to miss work"],[2957,3257,"because of me."],[4220,4291,"Listen, why don’t you"],[4291,4408,"take a hike, man?"],[4408,4483,"She gave you three of the"],[4483,4608,"best years of her life."],[4608,4767,"And what did you give her in return?"],[4767,4850,"Nothing but betrayal"],[4850,4938,"and heartbreak!"],[4938,5113,"I'll make it up to her."],[5113,5321,"Okay?"],[5321,5405,"Clark, I love her."],[5405,5605,"You love her?"],[5605,5730,"If you really love her,"],[5730,5826,"you let her go."],[5826,5926,"She's better off without you,"],[5926,6035,"you know that."],[6243,6402,"I won’t let go of Renee."],[6402,6531,"You won’t?"],[6531,6635,"What makes you even think you"],[6635,6719,"deserve her?"],[6952,7140,"All right, man."],[7140,7294,"I'll make you a deal."],[7294,7415,"You lead your team."],[7415,7494,"You beat us,"],[7494,7682,"and you become the champion."],[7682,7962,"Maybe I'll let you pursue Renee."],[8650,8812,"You have yourself a deal."]],"50":[[0,162,"You have yourself a deal."],[1664,1897,"Oh, my dear."],[1897,2035,"Are you all right?"],[2035,2127,"Levi!"],[2127,2377,"Mom, I'll be all right."],[2377,2548,"The injuries, they’re just..."],[2590,2677,"external."],[2711,2861,"Levi only got injured"],[2861,2961,"because he was trying"],[2961,3199,"to save Renee."],[3199,3299,"Here, Levi."],[3349,3457,"Have some cake."],[3457,3682,"It's going to make you feel better."],[3774,3937,"I’m allergic to strawberries."],[4421,4546,"That bitch again?"],[4546,4708,"Aren't you two divorced already?"],[4708,4808,"What does she want now,"],[4808,4867,"more money?"],[4867,5017,"Stop talking about Renee like that."],[5017,5238,"She's not what you think."],[5351,5413,"I'm starting to think"],[5413,5659,"that this divorce was a mistake."],[5659,5805,"You!"],[6118,6243,"Mom."],[6243,6364,"Since you can never see"],[6364,6535,"how amazing Renee is,"],[6535,6652,"I'll stop asking for your blessing."],[6748,6902,"As a matter of fact,"],[6902,7061,"my personal life"],[7061,7424,"has nothing to do with you."],[7424,7536,"Levi..."],[8024,8095,"Come on!"],[8562,8683,"Nora."],[8683,8933,"Nora, please. Oh!"],[8933,9217,"That useless fucking brat!"],[9217,9459,"Nora, don't be mad."],[9459,9613,"Maybe..."],[9613,9947,"Maybe Levi met with Renee"],[9947,10147,"because she's the Falcons"],[10147,10256,"head coach."],[10256,10372,"Wasn't he always trying"],[10372,10523,"to get into that club?"],[10523,10618,"You know,"],[10618,10781,"if we could convince the"],[10781,10985,"Falcons boss to fire Renee,"],[10985,11094,"then that fucking bitch"],[11094,11290,"would be out of his life forever."],[11290,11524,"Do you remember..."],[11524,11707,"Clark?"],[11707,11891,"Maybe if we can"],[11891,12233,"somehow prove that Renee is having"],[12266,12525,"inappropriate relationships"],[12525,12700,"with her players..."],[12783,13038,"Now we're talking."]],"51":[[617,763,"Jeez."],[763,988,"Who's that old guy with her?"],[988,1288,"Must be her new sugar daddy."],[1484,1747,"So what's the good news?"],[1747,1822,"I'm going to introduce"],[1822,1985,"you as the Molson heiress"],[1985,2173,"at the Bradley Cup final."],[2173,2477,"Daughter of the Falcons owner."],[2477,2640,"That might keep the vultures away."],[2923,3003,"I thought you wanted me to"],[3003,3190,"take photos of her and Clark."],[3190,3490,"I guess Ms. R never disappoints."],[3545,3645,"Yeah, did Clark ever"],[3645,3803,"find out who the driver was?"],[3803,3937,"Yeah,"],[3937,4079,"it's the same guy responsible"],[4079,4266,"for making Levi a vegetable."],[4266,4400,"What?"],[4400,4646,"God, who would do something like this?"],[4859,4971,"Wow."],[4971,5075,"Your new lover"],[5075,5330,"looks old enough to be your dad."],[5330,5630,"Have you no shame?"]],"52":[[0,100,"Your new lover"],[100,362,"looks old enough to be your dad."],[362,508,"What are you doing here, Madeline?"],[508,809,"I came to expose you."],[917,1180,"If these photos get out,"],[1180,1522,"you can kiss your career goodbye."],[1522,1876,"And Levi will never take you back."],[2331,2502,"Oh, Renee."],[2502,2731,"You didn't think we made copies?"],[2731,2932,"Tonight, after the finals,"],[2932,3178,"I'll show your boss these photos."],[3178,3315,"Enjoy your last night"],[3315,3465,"as the head coach."],[3499,3707,"Wow."],[3707,3762,"Be sure to stop by"],[3762,3966,"the VIP box tomorrow, Madeline."],[4154,4350,"Maybe I will!"],[4450,4633,"Maybe we will."],[4871,4938,"You know that"],[4938,5038,"with one word,"],[5038,5105,"I can make sure"],[5105,5217,"that she never sets foot"],[5217,5351,"in this country again, right?"],[5351,5384,"Yes,"],[5384,5684,"I know how powerful my dad is,"],[5684,5809,"but I kind of want to see how"],[5809,5976,"long she can go."],[5976,6122,"All right."]],"53":[[917,1217,"Levi Carlson, win this game."],[1292,1555,"Prove to Renee that you still can."],[2293,2444,"Mr. Molson, you have a visitor."],[2686,2798,"Come in."],[2882,3053,"I have proof"],[3053,3194,"that your head coach's"],[3194,3536,"personal life is a bit messy."],[3616,3703,"If you care about your"],[3703,3878,"team's reputation,"],[3878,4179,"you'll fire her immediately."],[4258,4479,"Are you threatening me?"],[4642,4779,"No."],[4779,4913,"No, I'm just saying"],[4913,5176,"Renee is not who you think she is."],[5176,5334,"Don't be fooled by her"],[5334,5513,"innocent looks."],[5513,5693,"And that sugar daddy of hers?"],[5693,5864,"A total tasteless perv."],[6218,6431,"Is that so?"],[6923,7148,"Where do you think you're going?"],[7148,7340,"Your little show's not over yet."]],"54":[[809,971,"Welcome, everyone,"],[971,1117,"to the most important"],[1117,1363,"event in the NHA..."],[1363,1564,"the Bradley Cup final!"],[1672,1847,"But before we begin,"],[1847,1939,"as the owner"],[1939,2131,"of the Boston Falcons,"],[2131,2198,"there's something"],[2198,2344,"I need to announce."],[2344,2560,"I know what he is going to say."],[2560,2715,"Your scandalous head coach"],[2715,2894,"is going to get fired."],[2894,2982,"What?"],[2982,3257,"Ms. R is not like that."],[3257,3399,"She'll be fired."],[3399,3553,"Just you watch."],[4283,4433,"Let me introduce you to"],[4433,4621,"my daughter."],[4904,5055,"What the fuck?"]],"55":[[4,108,"Hello, everyone."],[108,291,"I’m Renee Thompson Molson."],[291,367,"I'm the head"],[367,521,"coach of the Boston Falcons"],[521,579,"and the heir"],[579,713,"to the Molson group."],[713,896,"Wasn't she just accused of being a"],[896,984,"gold digger who"],[984,1134,"abandoned her family?"],[1134,1330,"That sounds ridiculous now."],[1330,1518,"Yeah, I mean, her dad’s literally"],[1518,1597,"one of the richest men"],[1597,1689,"on the Forbes list."],[1689,1872,"And her brother is number"],[1872,2043,"one star on the NHA right now."],[2043,2122,"Why the hell would she need"],[2122,2344,"to chase anyone for money?"],[2344,2427,"No!"],[2452,2627,"She really didn’t marry me"],[2627,2690,"for money?"],[2690,2798,"She married me..."],[2798,2911,"for love?"],[2911,3073,"I'm so sorry, Renee."],[3073,3182,"I should have seen everything"],[3182,3294,"you've done for me."],[3294,3432,"Now, before we get this game"],[3432,3549,"started, there's one"],[3549,3724,"final thing I’d like to share with you."],[4875,4975,"Do you all remember"],[4975,5067,"three years ago"],[5067,5230,"when Levi Carlson of the Boston"],[5230,5355,"Seagulls went down in a"],[5355,5501,"game and fell into a coma?"]],"56":[[91,166,"Slip this into"],[166,471,"Levi's drink before the game."],[471,675,"What are you trying to do?"],[675,809,"Levi's mom promised me"],[809,1038,"that if the team wins tonight,"],[1038,1226,"she'll make him marry me."],[1226,1413,"I need to bring his A-game."],[1484,1639,"You didn't mean to ruin his life,"],[1639,1747,"did you?"],[1747,1885,"But instead of owning up to it,"],[1885,2022,"you vanished the moment"],[2022,2139,"he got hurt."],[2139,2243,"And he finally fought"],[2243,2352,"his way back to the game."],[2352,2444,"And you acted like"],[2444,2656,"nothing happened."],[2656,2731,"You lied to him,"],[2731,3023,"and you sabotaged our marriage."],[3023,3169,"So the person you thought was"],[3169,3353,"your savior, was actually the one"],[3353,3536,"who put you in a coma?"],[3536,3595,"Dude,"],[3595,3807,"you divorced Renee for this woman?"],[3807,3953,"Shut up."],[4325,4491,"You bitch!"],[4491,4650,"So you were the one who ruined"],[4650,4796,"my son's life!"],[4796,4946,"Get her out of here."],[5668,5734,"Now that someone"],[5734,5897,"who clearly has no respect for"],[5897,6114,"the game has been escorted out,"],[6114,6222,"let's get back to what"],[6222,6406,"we all came here for."],[6406,6706,"The Bradley Cup final!"]],"57":[[83,337,"Tonight's Bradley Cup Final was"],[337,513,"one for the history books."],[513,642,"Though the Seagulls fell short"],[642,771,"to an underdog miracle,"],[771,896,"losing to the"],[896,1021,"powerhouse Falcons."],[1021,1213,"The defenseman Levi Carlson"],[1213,1388,"played the best game in his career."],[1388,1568,"To a worthy opponent!"],[2006,2122,"Cheers."],[2185,2310,"Cheers."],[2748,2952,"You know, Clark, it's funny..."],[2952,3157,"to think I thought my own brother"],[3157,3299,"in law was having an affair with"],[3299,3411,"my wife."],[3461,3745,"You know, I'll be honest, Carlson."],[3745,3933,"You earned my respect."],[3933,4079,"But I definitely still expect you"],[4079,4208,"to honor the deal."],[4208,4441,"Remember, no championship..."],[4441,4629,"No shot at my sister."],[4700,4925,"I may have lost this year,"],[4925,5109,"but the next year"],[5109,5242,"and the year after..."],[5242,5467,"As long as I can keep playing,"],[5467,5526,"I'll keep fighting"],[5526,5668,"for a championship."],[5734,5789,"Even if my"],[5789,5905,"opponent's a powerhouse"],[5905,6093,"like the Falcons."],[6093,6327,"I don't care."],[6327,6489,"I will always give it my all."],[6489,6660,"No matter what, for Renee."],[6840,6956,"All right, count me in."],[6956,7032,"Oh..."],[7140,7273,"Don’t think just because you’re a"],[7273,7353,"grandpa that can still play a"],[7353,7465,"decent game that I’ll just hand"],[7465,7595,"Renee over to you."],[7711,7903,"Oh, you piece of shit."],[7903,8058,"Cheers, boys."]],"58":[[471,663,"Levi!"],[663,971,"Marry me, right now."],[971,1101,"Or I'll kill her."],[1101,1309,"Maddie..."],[1309,1488,"just calm down, okay?"],[1605,1805,"Let Renee go."],[2252,2531,"Did I not make myself clear?"],[2606,2765,"Marry me,"],[2865,2973,"or she dies."],[2973,3107,"Of course."],[3107,3232,"Maddie, I'll marry you."],[3232,3324,"Look!"],[3324,3490,"I even prepared the ring."],[3490,3641,"Just for you."],[3766,3870,"Well then,"],[3870,4104,"come put it on me."],[4658,4783,"What’s taking so long–"],[4783,4842,"Oh!"],[4925,5088,"You bitch!"],[5372,5526,"Let, let go of it, Maddie."]],"59":[[250,371,"This is all my fault."],[371,462,"If I never would have chose"],[462,521,"that bar..."],[521,692,"None of this would've happened."],[809,988,"How's the patient, Doc?"],[988,1051,"The patient's"],[1051,1297,"life is no longer in danger."],[1297,1476,"But there's a chance of ending"],[1476,1630,"up in a vegetative state."],[1701,1939,"A vegetative state?"],[2135,2423,"Levi is in a coma again,"],[2423,2635,"because he saved my life?"],[2702,2840,"Mr. Carlson's condition"],[2840,3015,"is even worse than last time."],[3015,3132,"Unless there's a strong"],[3132,3332,"emotional trigger,"],[3332,3532,"he might not ever wake up again."],[3653,3791,"What?"],[4158,4450,"It'll be okay, sis."],[4450,4587,"It'll be okay."]],"60":[[2252,2460,"Please, Levi."],[2460,2652,"Wake up soon,"],[2652,2827,"okay?"],[4016,4229,"Dad, I’m gonna go see Levi."],[5226,5363,"I was such a fool"],[5363,5522,"for hurting Renee."],[5522,5822,"She's too good for our family."],[6297,6506,"Renee, I'm so sorry."],[8904,9046,"Uh..."],[9046,9209,"Guys?"],[9300,9509,"What is this?"],[9509,9680,"Renee,"],[9680,9855,"I'm here to propose."]],"61":[[229,321,"Dearly beloved,"],[321,433,"we are gathered here today"],[433,563,"in the eyes of God- - Wait, wait,"],[563,642,"wait a second!"],[642,838,"Are you serious right now?"],[934,1201,"Remember what the doctor said."],[1201,1355,"Levi needs a strong"],[1355,1655,"emotional trigger to wake up."],[2556,2698,"Levi Carlson,"],[2698,2932,"I'm about to marry another man."],[2932,3048,"If you really care about me,"],[3048,3190,"then wake up and stop me."],[3620,3703,"We are gathered here today"],[3703,3828,"in the eyes of God."],[3828,3937,"With these witnesses"],[3937,4054,"to join together,"],[4054,4149,"Edward Hughes"],[4149,4366,"and Renee Thompson Molson,"],[4366,4537,"in holy matrimony."],[5463,5572,"When we first got married,"],[5572,5722,"you were recovering from a coma."],[5722,6022,"We never had a real wedding."],[6022,6247,"Renee."],[6247,6431,"I promise"],[6431,6614,"when I wake up,"],[6614,6723,"I'll give you the grand wedding"],[6723,6915,"you deserve."],[7069,7253,"Then wake up for me,"],[7253,7390,"please."],[8704,8888,"Levi Carlson,"],[8888,8971,"if you don't wake up,"],[8971,9079,"I'm really gonna put on"],[9079,9275,"Edward's ring."],[9672,9922,"So please..."],[9922,10105,"wake up for me."]]}